Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.324 --> 00:00:12.683
A hearty welcome to Aha Yemi Ruchi.

00:00:13.085 --> 00:00:17.992
I feel lucky to be here,

00:00:18.342 --> 00:00:20.595
looking at the arrangements.

00:00:20.904 --> 00:00:22.824
So whats today's special?

00:00:23.786 --> 00:00:25.642
Its a Nellore famous dish, called Bommidayala Pulusu.

00:00:31.092 --> 00:00:38.404
Without a doubt, no body can cook fish the way Nellore people can.

00:00:38.566 --> 00:00:40.492
Tell me what all do we need to make this dish.

00:00:41.082 --> 00:00:44.266
The Ingredients.

00:00:44.506 --> 00:00:45.105
Bommidayalu (Channa marulius)

00:00:45.328 --> 00:00:46.041
tamarind,

00:00:46.041 --> 00:00:47.146
fenugreek,

00:00:47.146 --> 00:00:47.982
cumin seeds,

00:00:48.237 --> 00:00:49.111
green chillies,

00:00:49.111 --> 00:00:50.075
tomatoes,

00:00:50.075 --> 00:00:50.861
mustard,

00:00:51.282 --> 00:00:51.614
turmeric powder,

00:00:51.865 --> 00:00:52.606
chopped onions,

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:54.298
special chilli powder(chilli powder + garlic + cumin seeds + coriander seeds + fenugreek)

00:00:54.487 --> 00:00:55.060
chilli powder,

00:00:55.367 --> 00:00:55.646
curry leaf,

00:00:56.165 --> 00:00:56.899
coriander leaves,

00:00:56.899 --> 00:00:57.588
salt,

00:00:57.588 --> 00:00:58.405
and refined oil,

00:01:03.636 --> 00:01:05.608
The procedure.

00:01:05.608 --> 00:01:07.712
Heat oil in a bowl,

00:01:07.732 --> 00:01:08.883
and add fenugreek, mustard,

00:01:08.883 --> 00:01:09.974
cumin seeds,

00:01:09.974 --> 00:01:11.896
green chillies and chopped onions.

00:01:12.318 --> 00:01:13.177
And fry them for a while,

00:01:13.177 --> 00:01:16.103
now add tomatoes and cook for a while.

00:01:16.237 --> 00:01:18.786
Later, add turmeric powder, chilli powder,

00:01:18.786 --> 00:01:25.248
and spcial chilli powder (chilli powder + garlic + cumin seeds + coriander seeds + fenugreek),

00:01:26.152 --> 00:01:27.651
and salt and fry for a while.

00:01:28.511 --> 00:01:32.157
Now add the fish and fry so that the fish are not mashed.

00:01:32.260 --> 00:01:37.317
Later, add tamarind juice and cook the mixture for fifteen minutes.

00:01:37.453 --> 00:01:39.173
Finally add the curry leaves.

00:01:39.213 --> 00:01:42.089
Once thoroughly cooked, garnish with coriander leaves.

00:01:42.817 --> 00:01:49.978
The rich and tasty Bommidayala Pulusu is ready to serve!

00:02:04.757 --> 00:02:06.897
Its heavenly!

00:02:06.897 --> 00:02:08.363
it tastes amazing!

